abstract: Six more horses have been found fatally shot near a strip mine site in eastern Kentucky, according to authorities.
snippet: Six more horses have been found fatally shot near a strip mine site in eastern Kentucky, according to authorities.
lead_paragraph: PRESTONSBURG, Ky. — Six more horses have been found fatally shot near a strip mine site in eastern Kentucky, according to authorities.
headline_main: 6 More Horses Found Shot to Death in Eastern Kentucky
headline_print_headline: 6 More Horses Found Shot to Death in Eastern Kentucky

abstract: The federal prosecutor leading a review of the origins of the Russia inquiry has a reputation for keeping his mouth shut. At a sensitive moment, he didn’t.
snippet: The federal prosecutor leading a review of the origins of the Russia inquiry has a reputation for keeping his mouth shut. At a sensitive moment, he didn’t.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Whether investigating charges of torture by the C.I.A., rolling up an organized crime network or prosecuting crooked government officials, John H. Durham, the veteran federal prosecutor named by Attorney General William P. Barr to investigate the origins of the Russia inquiry, burnished his reputation for impartiality over the years by keeping his mouth closed about his work.
